data.description: This spacious 5 Bedroom 3 Bath home is ideally located in southwest Visalia. You'll be just moments away from shopping, schools, and all the amenities the area has to offer. Step into an expansive interior spanning approximately 2,500 square feet, featuring 5 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, and a variety of living spaces designed for both family living and grand entertaining. The remodeled kitchen is perfect for hosting dinner parties and comes equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, double ovens, and custom cabinetry. Enjoy movie nights or host game days in either the living room or family room nestled next the cozy fireplace. The spacious upstairs master suite provides a private retreat with a walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom with double sinks. It opens to a balcony offering views of the large built-in pool. This home also boasts a 2nd master bedroom on the main level with back yard access to the restroom.  This home has also been updated with new energy efficient windows installed throughout. Don't miss your chance to own this extraordinary home. Schedule a private viewing today and experience 3609 W. Evergreen Ave. for yourself. Call for more details or to arrange a showing.
